    act_title: 'Prologue',
    producers: 'Joe Kocur',
    act_description:
     'Joe Kocur was a hockey enforcer for the Detroit Red Wings and the New York Rangers, back in the heyday of hockey\'s tough guys. Kocur talks to host Ira Glass about how a good enforcer keeps other players in line. If you want to read more stories about Joe Kocur\'s life as a hockey enforcer, it\'s all in a new book called The Bruise Brothers, about Kocur and his teammate (and fellow enforcer) Bob Probert. The book is only available at immortalinvestments.com. (5 minutes)',
